Spray the bottom of a 4- to 6-quart pot with nonstick spray. Add the onions, celery, garlic and curry powder. Stir to mix, then cover and cook over medium heat for 5 minutes. Add carrots, corn, tomatoes and broth. Bring to a boil. Cover and reduce heat to low. Simmer for 20 minutes. Add peas, tofu, and spinach leaves. Stir and simmer 5 minutes.